result.title: Invitation to the CodeChef SnackDown 2015 Open Elimination Round on CodeChef
result.content:
CodeChef invites you to participate in the CodeChef SnackDown 2015 Open Elimination Round, which is an open contest for those who could not proceed to the elimination round.

Time: 12th June 2015 (2300 hrs) to 13th June 2015 (0200 hrs). (Indian Standard Time — +5:30 GMT) — Check your timezone.

Details: http://www.codechef.com/SD15ELOP

Registration: It is a team contest, so you need to register your teams first to take part in the contest. To register your team, login to your CodeChef account and go to: http://www.codechef.com/teams/register/SD15ELOP. If you don't have a CodeChef account, get one here. The registrations are open till the end of the contest.

  • Problem Setters : Cherrytree (Sergey Kulik) sentinel45 (Ankit Srivastava) and iscsi (Istvan Nagy)
  • Editorialist: kevinsogo (Kevin Atenzia)
  • Problem Tester: kevinsogo (Kevin Atenzia) and gediiiiiii (Gedi Zheng)
  • Contest Admin: I_lost_my_handle (Praveen Dhinwa)
  • Russian Translator : Cherrytree (Sergey Kulik)
  • Mandarin Translator: gediiiiiii (Gedi Zheng)
  • Vietnamese Translator: khanhptnk (Khanh Xuan Nguyen)

It promises to deliver on an interesting set of algorithmic problems with something for all.

Good Luck! Hope to see you participating.
